p.d: Chanti is about to set off on the journey of his life in the company of his girlfriend, Sabrina. Together they are heading for Laos, Chanti's native country. An opportunity for him to revisit his past. Together they will share moments they'll never forget and encounters rich in emotion. Directed by: Katrin Blum, Oliver Roth, Karen Ballmer (season 2, Switzerland, 2019)
